data.name: Onslaught of the Fire Kings
data.desc: If your opponent controls a monster and you control no monsters: Special Summon 1 FIRE Beast, Beast-Warrior, or Winged Beast monster from your Deck. Its effects are negated, also it is destroyed during the End Phase. You can only activate 1 "Onslaught of the Fire Kings" per turn.

card_sets.set_name: Onslaught of the Fire Kings Structure Deck
